11. Qxd8 Rxd8 12. dxe5 Re8 13. O-O dxe5 $11) 6... Nxe4 7. Nxe4 (7. Nf7 $2 Qh4 {
Threatening to win the bishop with ...Nc5.} 8. Nxh8 Qxf2+ 9. Kd1 Qxg2 10. Re1
f4 $19 {with a decisive attack.}) 7... Na5 $1 (7... fxe4 $2 8. Bf7+ Ke7 {
Christensen,B-Jensen,I Denmark 1981 (½- ½, 57)} 9. d4 $16) 8. Qa4+ (8. Bf7+
