11. Qxb5+ Bd7 12. Qd5 f4 13. Ne4 Bc6 14. Qe6+ Be7 15. d3 Qc7 16. O-O Bd7 $5 17.
Qd5 Bc6 $13) (5. exf5 {is examined in Line 5.}) 5... f4 {With the bishop on b5,
