Nxd4 10. cxd4 Nf6 $17) 7... Bd6 8. Re1 Nf6 9. Nxe5 O-O {Black has a big
advance in development, ensuring him enough compensation for the pawn (s) .}
10. Bxc6 (10. d4 Nxe5 11. dxe5 Ng4 12. Qxd5+ (12. exd6 Qxd6 13. f4 (13. g3 Nxf2
$1 14. Qd4 Nh3+ 15. Kg2 c6 16. Bf1 c5 17. Qd1 g6 $19 {with an overwhelming
